CatDescriptText: The butcher shop or grocery has a neon sign in the window advertising cut up poultry and fresh fish, with a picture of a fish rather than the word.  Isaly's window has advertisement for peanut squares $ .59.
TitMainTitle: Three men, two standing between a butcher shop or grocery store and Isaly's, one holding document, small sign on wall above them reads "re-elect Ryan for alderman, elect Hardy for constable, 13th Ward Democratic"
